description:
The Abortion Controversy - Program 2: Abortion Trauma - Dianne Wagner’s Story (Part 2) -  Steve Wohlberg interviews Dianne Wagner of Mafgia Ministry. Dianne had two abortions, suffered unimaginable guilt, pain, and other “Post Abortion Syndrome” symptoms, and finally found hope and healing through God’s forgiveness, love and grace. Emotional. Inspirational. Life-changing!
